                     <interp inst="t18170416-235-person1727" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker, and live in Bow-street, Bloomsbury. On the 28th of March, I took a tablecloth in pledge from the prisoner for 15s, and on the 5th of April I took another table-cloth-the duplicates found<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181704160064"></xptr>on the prisoner are mine. They were pledged in the name of Richards, Gray's-inn-lane.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18170416-235-person1728">
