                     <interp inst="t18170416-235-person1728" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker, living in Tooley-street. I have a table-cloth, which was pledged at my house, on the 26th of March, in the name of Best.</p>
               <p>HANNAH BEST. I received that table-cloth from the prisoner - He told me to pledge it, and said it was his own.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
